column5: Thanks Gord..  et all !  http://apps.facebook.com/ereadwithindigo/entry?id=1249
You've moved her up to 4th... keep it going right 'till midnight Sunday night.  It's keeping her mind occupied and that's the goal of this whole thing. Chemo again Monday am.  Thanks folks!!
311 and risin' fast captain !!!!!!!!!!!!!! Warp drive has been engaged

Too bad for the automated cheaters... 1st place jumped 600 votes in just over a day.. hasn't moved one vote in 28 hours.. they're sittin there scared as the original first place auto voter got toasted and people are starting to leave comments on their picture. There is now a picture that was just uploaded about 12 minutes ago that is going thru 360 votes already... hmmmmmm...     Regardless... those are providing entertainment for Jen as well...
Wayne, unfortunately there are a lot of 'Auto like' scripts available out there that people can use..

I know Bill... it's too bad, though hopefully they audit them out and make it "fair".. .. well as fair a popularity contest can be! lol  It's just stuff to keep Jen going... I've gotta thank publicly the three individuals that offered Jen eReaders directly !! From here on the board... salty, ctdd2006 and young one's friends .

You'll probably need clearance from sick kids to make a donation of such devices though. So check into that and then spark up a new thread to see if it can be done. I've been waiting 3 months to find out if I can buy a $100 microwave for the 11th floor pantry of Mount Sinai to no avail.. yet I know someone put a $50 one from Walmart in the nurses station ..instead of the pantry where they blew it up!
